Vaughn, HBO Max, and Sockness

11-12 February 2021

Naught talks to Praetor about Larry Vaughn. Naught asks if there is a plan for Vaughn. Praetor considers providing Vaughn's number, though remarks that stirring the pot is silly. Chris instead says he will give Naught the number and that he is done with Vaughn.

Chris changes the subject to the weather, noting the snow and that he must shovel the walk. Chris also talks about the television shows Girls and Sex & the City which have been added to HBO Max. He claims that one of the male characters from Sex & the City was a simp and then married the woman he had simped over. Chris compares himself, saying he used to be a real simp. He exclaims, "Hormones get crazy as Woahly Fuck."

Later, Chris shifts to the Dimensional Merge and inquires about Sockness's neighborhood, as Chris considers it a hotspot for the Merge. Though he brings up Sockness, Chris couches it by prefacing with, "not to beat on a retarded, essentially dead, horse".

19 February 2021[1]
